the scripts in active should be put in ~/pg_hack/ha/ of both active and standby
the scripts in nfs should be put in ~ of nfs

init experiment

0.prepare the nfs
1.set global_var.sh in both active and standby
2.set recovery.conf in standby.sh
3.call initenv.sh in both active and standby
4.call copyha.sh to init shadow environment. Or call copysingle.sh to init standalone
